name: CoreAPI WF_Definition
description: API to access results of Planet 9 workflow definitions
about:
Description

Planet 9 Workflow_Definitions maintains the list workflow Definitions.

API WF_Definition is the Planet 9 API to access the API of Planet 9 workflows definitions and the operations performed on them.

You can use this API WF_Definition in your app to add, delete and update the workflows.

Every app must have the right roles (permissions) and authentication that enables access to the Workflows API. 

Workflow is a complex task if created by App, for ease, we recommend to use Planet 9 Workflow UI.

Operations Performed

List

Get the workflows definitions list 

ResponseList(array)- Definition                         

Get

Get the corresponding to id workflow definition

RequestID
ResponseGet/Start(object)-Definition         


Delete

Delete the workflow definition

RequestID                          

Save

Save the definition

RequestGet/Start(object)-Definition
